name: Nick Halden
description: I am active, fit, kind, generous, a gentleman with a high level of energy and integrity and a great sense of humor. Faith and family are very important to me. I like all sports especially football and hockey. I consider myself a person that is open minded and non-judgmental and am a positive person, that looks forward not behind. I’ve learned a lot out of adversity but that has made me a very strong, determined, caring person.
